    <title type="html"><![CDATA[knife did not create any data bag]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.ahwkong.com/post/2015/02/25/knife-did-not-create-any-data-bag/"/>
    <updated>2015-02-25T11:36:00+11:00</updated>
    <id>http://www.ahwkong.com/post/2015/02/25/knife-did-not-create-any-data-bag</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I want to create an offline cookbook. I want to create a user databag to use the <code>users</code> recipe. I ran</p>

<pre><code>knife data bag create users
</code></pre>

<p>but it created nothing in the databag folder.</p>

<p>It turns out I need to run it in local mode and give it a user name:</p>

<pre><code>knife data bag create users myuser -z
</code></pre>
]]></content>
